track_notes: This summit is not a must, it can be done when back from F/AM-477, the walk is not fine because of the small trees and there is no path. May be we can use the west crest... ill try later

This is not realy a must. The track is not difficult, but you have to look out the path which is difficult to found sometimes. Plenty room for antenna. There are some goats on summits and a dog.
Nice ponorama to the Mercantour.
